So that's what you're worried about.

114
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,000
Well... how about this?

115
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:18,830
Focus mainly on taking care of Mr. Hu,

116
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:19,870
and treat our work as secondary.

117
00:05:19,870 --> 00:05:21,310
After all,
the work is just between us two.

118
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,870
We can plan and schedule our time.

119
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,390
Charity case now?

120
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:27,390
So you mean I don't have to work

121
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:29,430
