123
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,720
-I know what you mean. - I'm saying...

124
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,630
I know.

125
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,920
You're someone who understands gratitude.

126
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,510
The problem is with me, you know?

127
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:38,870
I have my pride.

128
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,750
I can't stand people pitying me.

129
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,950
