133
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:53,160
We talked about this.

134
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,600
Stop joking like this.

135
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:55,950
I'm not joking.

136
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,830
I'm serious.

137
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,600
