already got their money back.

196
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,150
So I added someone
from that. investment company

197
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,790
A Mr. Wang.

198
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,120
That young man told me

199
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:49,240
