we need to pay taxes first.

200
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:50,600
Pay taxes?

201
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,870
On our own money?

202
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:55,670
Why pay taxes?

203
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,270
That's what they said.

204
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,510
But Wang explained

205
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,390
