209
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,790
How much tax?

210
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,360
Twenty percent of the principal.

211
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:17,200
And they want us to transfer it first.

212
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,360
Twenty percent.

213
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,630
That's 100,000 yuan.

214
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,510
