223
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:48,120
I checked all their Moments.

224
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:49,720
They look legit.

225
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,360
Alright.

226
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:55,910
This time,

227
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,720
