243
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:46,870
My son shares my surname.

244
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:47,670
Right.

245
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:48,120
Right.

246
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,550
