we need to ask more questions.

253
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,750
See?

254
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,420
[Wang Xiuhong's ID]

255
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,750
My son shares my surname.

256
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,550
No problem, right?

257
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,000
