267
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:50,790
Hu Manli.

268
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:52,440
My newly place isn't far from here.

269
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,750
If you need any help,

270
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:55,870
you can always come to me.

271
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,670
Xiaozhou,

272
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,240
