284
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:31,630
Baodan.

285
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,720
I'll miss you, Baodan.

286
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:35,240
Coming down now.

287
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:37,150
You can't forget about me.

288
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:43,960
Baodan, I'll miss you.

289
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,150
Enough of that.

290
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:46,360
It's not like
we'll never see each other again.

291
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:47,550
We live so close.

292
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:48,960
If anything comes up,

293
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,480
you can still turn to Xiaozhou.

294
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:04,390
Then I'll be off.

295
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:05,750
Let me walk you out.

296
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,550
It's really heavy.

297
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,270
Here, put it on my back.

298
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,080
Xiaozhou,

299
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:34,320
send me the address.

300
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:35,360
I'll visit you.

301
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,960
Already sent it.

302
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:39,510
Alright, go back now.

303
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,030
Be a good boy.

304
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,080
Go on.

305
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,600
Mom.

306
00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:58,510
You don't want Xiaozhou to leave either.

307
00:13:58,910 --> 00:13:59,320
Right?

308
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,200
Of course.

309
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,120
You'll grow attached to a pet,

310
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,790
let alone a person.

311
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,030
Then I'll call him back.

312
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:08,630
Sit down.

313
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:12,910
I don't think he wants to leave either.

314
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,480
Sleeping arrangements?

315
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:16,120
I can squeeze in with him.

316
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,390
No need.

317
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,600
Don't see him unless necessary.

318
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:24,240
But that's not what you just told him.

319
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,750
He's doing well in his career now.

320
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:28,030
I can't hold him back.

321
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,240
Can't be a burden to him.

322
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,550
But shouldn't friends

323
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:31,910
help each other out?

324
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,480
You need him right now.

325
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,550
You don't have to
play the tragic hero, okay?

326
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:36,480
No.

327
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:37,480
I don't need anyone.

328
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,030
I can manage by myself.

329
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,790
Anyhow, from now on,

330
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:42,630
don't see him

331
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,080
without my permission.

332
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,870
You're so annoying.

333
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:49,320
You barely ate breakfast.
Drink your milk.

334
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:49,960
No.

335
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,870
Why is Wang's number disconnected?

336
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,390
Try message him.

337
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:17,960
Why did he block me? What...

338
00:15:20,390 --> 00:15:21,080
Well...

339
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,440
Ask those who received money
in the group chat

340
00:15:24,550 --> 00:15:26,550
if they have other
contact info for Wang.

341
00:15:33,790 --> 00:15:34,120
What?

342
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,750
How come this group got disbanded?

343
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:38,150
It's over.

344
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:39,550
We're finished now.

345
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:41,270
Lost even our funeral savings.

346
00:15:42,390 --> 00:15:43,870
Hurry, call Zhiyuan.

347
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,120
Get him to figure something out.

348
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:47,150
You can't get

349
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:49,790
a word out of him if you tried.

350
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,510
What's the point telling him anything?

351
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,120
Back then, we always had Manli

352
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:55,840
to handle these things for us.

353
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:56,750
How come now you...

354
00:15:58,480 --> 00:15:59,080
Manli?

355
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,270
Right. Go to Manli.

356
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,550
She doesn't have to help us now.

357
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:05,480
Can't worry about that anymore.

358
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,200
When that investment scheme collapsed,

359
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:09,440
Manli helped us
find the financial company.

360
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:10,840
She knows a lot of people.

361
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,360
She must know what's going on.

362
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:13,790
Let's go.

363
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,150
Hurry up!

364
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:16,390
Go!

365
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,480
Hurry up and eat the shrimp.

366
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,390
Finished your homework?

367
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:38,060
Yes.

368
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:41,000
But I can't solve two math problems.

369
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,550
I think...

370
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,200
No, you don't.

371
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:47,960
Look it up online yourself.

372
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:51,200
But my school teacher
came up with the question.

373
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,240
No solution online.

374
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,600
Then ask your classmates or teachers.

375
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,390
Could it be Xiaozhou?

376
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:09,480
Daer.

377
00:17:11,350 --> 00:17:12,110
Grandpa, Grandma.

378
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:13,960
Why are you here?

379
00:17:14,350 --> 00:17:14,880
What?

380
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,960
Your tone doesn't sound welcoming.

381
00:17:18,350 --> 00:17:19,000
No, not at all.

382
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,030
Hello, you guys.

383
00:17:22,350 --> 00:17:23,110
Welcome.

384
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:24,510
Come in.

385
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:24,830
Okay.

386
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:29,400
There's a homeowners' meeting tonight.
I need to go to

387
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,480
the property management office.

388
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,110
You stay home and keep

389
00:17:33,750 --> 00:17:34,960
Grandpa and Grandma company, okay?

390
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:37,440
No rush, Manli.

391
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,070
We...

392
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,880
came to see you.

393
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,200
Me?

394
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:29,830
Well.

395
00:18:30,830 --> 00:18:32,790
You might have fallen victim
to telecom fraud.

396
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:36,790
That can't be.

397
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,240
If they were scammers

398
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:40,960
how would they know

399
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:43,590
about the financial products
we bought years ago,

400
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,830
our home address,

401
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:46,480
and even our ID numbers?

402
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:47,640
It's obvious.

403
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:50,070
The financial company
sold your information.

404
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,350
That's impossible.

405
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:54,720
Manli.

406
00:18:55,550 --> 00:18:56,350
Back then when you

407
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:58,070
helped us recover
those financial products,

408
00:18:58,480 --> 00:18:59,400
the other party said

409
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:01,000
they would take full responsibility.

410
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,550
Seven or eight years have passed.

411
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,680
I reckon

412
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,960
it should be our turn by now.

413
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:08,440
You've been to this company before.

414
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,550
Could you help us go ask?

415
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,000
I suggest you report to

416
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,440
the police immediately.

417
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:17,480
There might still be hope of
recovering the money.

418
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,550
That Wang

419
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,590
was actually quite decent.

420
00:19:22,350 --> 00:19:23,550
He couldn't be a scammer, could he?

421
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,960
Besides, we're

422
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:27,480
not those uneducated elderly folks.

423
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,790
We're not that easily fooled.

424
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:32,830
Alright then.

425
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:33,720
In that case,

426
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:35,550
you go ask Wang again?

427
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:37,000
I...

428
00:19:37,310 --> 00:19:37,680
You're...

429
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:39,310
Manli.

430
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:42,790
Do you not want to
help with this matter?

431
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,720
It's not that I don't want to help.

432
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:47,350
I simply don't know how to help.

433
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:49,720
Manli.

434
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:53,510
Are you still upset about the breakup?

435
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,070
That's completely unrelated.

436
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:58,640
It's been so long already.

437
00:19:59,240 --> 00:19:59,830
I understand.

438
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:01,640
Back then,

439
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,680
Zhiyuan who abandoned you

440
00:20:03,790 --> 00:20:04,960
and started a new family.

441
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:07,070
Now his current wife

442
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,750
is about to give birth soon.

443
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:11,310
But let us make this clear.

444
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:14,030
This money is for Daer.

445
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:15,510
So,

446
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,000
take it seriously.

447
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:21,400
I appreciate your kindness.

448
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:23,720
I appreciate it on Daer's behalf too.

449
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,200
But Dingding is my son.

450
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:27,790
I can support him.

451
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,440
No need for you to worry.

452
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,350
It's getting late.

453
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,070
Maybe you should head back first.

454
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:39,960
Dingding has school tomorrow.

455
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,510
Look at you.

456
00:20:43,270 --> 00:20:44,750
You're so cold-hearted.

457
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,400
That's not appropriate.

458
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:50,680
There are things I didn't want to say.

459
00:20:51,270 --> 00:20:52,790
But since this is your attitude,

460
00:20:53,350 --> 00:20:53,790
fine,

461
00:20:54,750 --> 00:20:56,270
then we won't hold back either.

462
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:59,960
The root of this current trouble

463
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:01,510
lies with you.

464
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:05,750
The root lies with me?

465
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:06,790
You must be mistaken.

466
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:08,720
Not a penny of

467
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:11,240
your money ever made it into my account.

468
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,160
That can't be right.

469
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:15,030
Back then, the one million
relocation compensation

470
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:16,550
was intended to use for our retirement.

471
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:18,480
Then 500K vanished in
financial management.

472
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,000
It was you who suggested

473
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,200
to use the remaining 500K

474
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,790
to buy an education annuity for Daer.

475
00:21:23,310 --> 00:21:25,110
And you'd take care of
our retirement, right?

476
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:28,160
Now that you've split with Zhiyuan,

477
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:30,590
the money belonging to me and my husband

478
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:32,640
should be returned to us.

479
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:36,830
These are two separate matters.

480
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:37,920
That money was used

481
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:39,720
to buy insurance for Dingding.

482
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:42,160
Whether I'm with Ding Zhiyuan or not

483
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,750
has nothing to do with the child.

484
00:21:44,590 --> 00:21:46,030
He's still your grandson, isn't he?

485
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:47,790
That's not how it works.

486
00:21:48,310 --> 00:21:50,200
Once the money was given, how it's used

487
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,640
was entirely up to you.

488
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:53,000
We had no way of knowing.

489
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:54,350
Moreover,

490
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:57,000
raising children is parents' responsibility.

491
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,440
Grandparents helping is a blessing.

492
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,030
Not helping is only natural.

493
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:04,510
Since you won't help us
get the money back,

494
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:07,200
we won't help raise your child either.

495
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:14,270
Coming.

496
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:19,830
Hello, your delivery.

497
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:20,270
Thank you.

498
00:23:02,830 --> 00:23:04,720
Give it a good shake
to get the fruit pieces.

499
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:06,960
Having hot pot?

500
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:08,720
Amazing.

501
00:23:10,030 --> 00:23:12,030
You've been eating here
for free for so long.

502
00:23:12,830 --> 00:23:14,830
But today's dish is special.

503
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:15,640
It costs extra

504
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:17,480
fifty.

505
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:18,920
Who would you like to pay?

506
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,400
I eat for free?

507
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,830
Fine, I won't argue with you.

508
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,270
Lucky I'm smart.

509
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:25,720
I smelled hotpot.

510
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:27,110
I knew you'd pull this trick.

511
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:28,350
I ordered takeout.

512
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:32,070
Here.

513
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:35,160
Hotpot.

514
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:39,070
What's so great about hotpot?

515
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,030
Spicy stew!

516
00:23:59,790 --> 00:24:00,830
Want me to share some with you?

517
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,640
I'm not like your mom,
I won't charge you.

518
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,350
No thanks.

519
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:05,830
Haven't you read?

520
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,160
What?

521
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,160
What? Show me.

522
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:14,000
Show me.

523
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:22,270
Delivery guy

524
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:25,310
spit in the spicy stew,

525
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:26,920
then shook it up.

526
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:32,350
Xiaozhou.

527
00:24:33,030 --> 00:24:33,720
It's fine.

528
00:24:34,550 --> 00:24:35,510
News is just news.

529
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:36,920
You... enjoy it.

530
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,030
The delivery guys around here

531
00:24:39,030 --> 00:24:40,070
probably wouldn't do that.

532
00:24:40,270 --> 00:24:40,880
Yeah.

533
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,750
I... I'm not very hungry,
I'll eat later.

534
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:45,750
Um... Xiaozhou.

535
00:24:46,310 --> 00:24:47,480
Want some juice?

536
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:48,110
It's free.

537
00:24:48,350 --> 00:24:48,720
No need.

538
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,200
You're just being stubborn.

539
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,030
I'm giving you a chance now.

540
00:24:56,550 --> 00:24:57,480
If you beg me now,

541
00:24:58,350 --> 00:24:59,350
I can still give you

542
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:00,510
the original price of fifty.

543
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:09,830
Home-cooked meals

544
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:11,350
are both delicious and healthy.

545
00:25:11,350 --> 00:25:12,030
Right, Dingding?

546
00:25:13,110 --> 00:25:13,830
Use this strainer.

547
00:25:14,590 --> 00:25:15,240
I picked it up.

548
00:25:22,590 --> 00:25:23,400
Shall I pay here?

549
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,270
No problem.

550
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:27,750
Let me get you a bowl.

551
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:29,550
I'll grab another cup.

552
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,510
He gets drinks with the meal?

553
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:38,680
It's a combo.

554
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,310
Sir, enjoy.

555
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:18,030
I happened to run into Mr. Huang and

556
00:26:18,550 --> 00:26:19,440
mentioned it in passing.

557
00:26:19,590 --> 00:26:20,240
Mr. Huang

558
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,750
knows someone at the Health Bureau.

559
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:23,750
They called, and there

560
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:24,590
happened to be a vacant bed.

561
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:25,350
So Dad...

562
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,240
I mean,

563
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:28,200
Daer's grandpa got admitted.

564
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:30,240
Don't be too modest.

565
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:32,240
For you to ask someone for help,

566
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:33,830
I appreciate the gesture.

567
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:36,750
Let me buy you to dinner
after this is over.

568
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,400
Hu Manli, is it because

569
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:44,200
I'm in your way?

570
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,830
Some things

571
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,680
are better left unsaid.

572
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,790
I'll say this one last time.

573
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:09,550
That money was used
to buy insurance for Dingding.

574
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,310
You agreed to it initially, didn't you?

